(1, 1, '2016-08-03 01:33:42', '2016-08-03 01:33:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">Well, the first thing I guess is to start by sharing a little bit about myself. In short, I am a military spouse, a mother of two and a jack of all trades, therefore I get very little sleep....regularly. I like to learn how to fix my car problems, make new meals for my family, coding (learning via <a href="http://www.skillcrush.com" target="_blank">Skillcrush</a>), analyze data and read a variety of books. Currently, I am doing Zumba three times a week and am burning more calories just keeping up, rather than because I am so fabulously skilled at following routines. If I do it on the Wii, does that make me a gamer too? Probably not, since the Wii has already been replaced by the newer console - Wii U. Welcome to my site! Sit back, relax and prepare for a <strong>LOT</strong> of laughs.</p>', 'THIS is the beginning!  Wow! Where to start?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beginning', '', '', '2016-08-15 19:06:47', '2016-08-16 02:06:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
