(47365, 1, '2016-08-24 14:10:47', '2016-08-24 21:10:47', 'Wow, impressed aren''t you!  Now I have added a little bit of CSS.  I have Lists, multiple backgrounds, etc.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-47352" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-24-at-1.50.30-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2016-08-24 at 1.50.30 PM" width="1503" height="1100" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWow, impressed aren''t you!  Now I have added a little bit of CSS.  I have Lists, multiple backgrounds, etc.', 'My Second Made-From-Scratch Webpage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47351-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-24 14:10:47', '2016-08-24 21:10:47', '', 47351, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2016/08/24/47351-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(47366, 1, '2016-08-24 14:11:06', '2016-08-24 21:11:06', 'Wow, impressed aren''t you!  Now I have added a little bit of CSS.  I have Lists, multiple backgrounds, etc.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-47352" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-24-at-1.50.30-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2016-08-24 at 1.50.30 PM" width="1503" height="1100" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'My Second Made-From-Scratch Webpage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47351-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-24 14:11:06', '2016-08-24 21:11:06', '', 47351, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2016/08/24/47351-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(47367, 1, '2016-08-24 14:12:37', '2016-08-24 21:12:37', 'Here is the page I build when I learned how to work with JavaScript:\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-47355" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-24-at-1.56.27-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2016-08-24 at 1.56.27 PM" width="1154" height="599" />\r\n\r\nThis is only a screenshot, but if you haaaadd clicked that ok button, this is what would have appeared:\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-47356" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-24-at-1.56.41-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2016-08-24 at 1.56.41 PM" width="1008" height="589" />', 'Adding JavaScript', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47354-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-24 14:12:37', '2016-08-24 21:12:37', '', 47354, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2016/08/24/47354-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(47368, 1, '2016-08-24 14:15:13', '2016-08-24 21:15:13', 'I am a jack-of-all-trades kind of person. I have worked in the military benefits industry, cosmetics, clothing retail, and recently with non-profits. Along with a B.A. in Psychology, I have a M.A. in International Relations. With over 15 years of work experience and a few more with my father''s business before that, I have a secret about myself: I love people! I enjoy helping people building webpages, find resources, establish goals and make connections.  Now I am in business for myself as a <strong>Web Developer</strong>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here is where everything started:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/portfolio/first-made-scratch-webpage/">My First Made-From-Scratch webpage</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/portfolio/second-made-scratch-webpage/">My Second Made-From-Scratch webpage</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/portfolio/adding-javascript/">Adding JavaScript to my webpage</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Portfolio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47330-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-24 14:15:13', '2016-08-24 21:15:13', '', 47330, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2016/08/24/47330-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
